g.text: Execution Traces: Maximal Munch vs Prefix Match

div.h3: The Critical Rule: Scan First, Lookup Second

ol.li: Greedy Scan: _scan_identifier consumes every valid character first.
Atomic Context: The scanner does not check the keyword map until the boundary is reached.
Prevention: This prevents iffy from being incorrectly broken into KEYWORD(if) + IDENTIFIER(fy).
